[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":403},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F09\u002F29\u002Flearn-hexo-16-minos-theme\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F09\u002F29\u002Flearn-hexo-16-minos-theme\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F09\u002F29\u002Flearn-hexo-16-minos-theme\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F09\u002F29\u002Flearn-hexo-16-minos-theme\u002F":380,"related:\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F09\u002F29\u002Flearn-hexo-16-minos-theme\u002F":389},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20200929\u002F422561814\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":363,"date":364,"description":19,"extension":365,"lang":366,"meta":367,"navigation":368,"path":369,"readingMinutes":370,"seo":371,"standalone":372,"stem":373,"tags":374,"tldr":377,"updated":364,"url":378,"__hash__":379},"content\u002Fen\u002FHexo\u002Flearn-hexo-16-minos-theme.md","(16) Learning Hexo from Scratch - Themes: minos","4185652241",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":357},"minimark",[11,16,20,24,27,34,37,54,69,89,100,109,116,122,125,134,137,142,146,157,160,176,191,276,291,297,300,311,315,331,337,347,353],[12,13,15],"h2",{"id":14},"intro","Intro",[17,18,19],"p",{},"Next up is installing the minos theme. This one's a bit more landmine-prone than the others.",[12,21,23],{"id":22},"installing-minos","Installing minos",[17,25,26],{},"The theme install process is mostly the same, but a few themes have their own quirks during setup that catch people out.",[17,28,29],{},[30,31],"img",{"alt":32,"src":33},"Landmines, source: internet","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E8%B8%A9%E9%9B%B7.jpg",[17,35,36],{},"Here's the clone command:",[38,39,44],"pre",{"className":40,"code":41,"language":42,"meta":43,"style":43},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","git clone https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fppoffice\u002Fhexo-theme-minos.git themes\u002Fminos\n","cmd","",[45,46,47],"code",{"__ignoreMap":43},[48,49,52],"span",{"class":50,"line":51},"line",1,[48,53,41],{},[17,55,56,57,60,61,64,65,68],{},"Same as before — update ",[45,58,59],{},"theme"," in ",[45,62,63],{},"hexo\u002F_config.yml"," to ",[45,66,67],{},"minos",":",[38,70,74],{"className":71,"code":72,"language":73,"meta":43,"style":43},"language-yml shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","theme: minos\n","yml",[45,75,76],{"__ignoreMap":43},[48,77,78,81,85],{"class":50,"line":51},[48,79,59],{"class":80},"sKpQp",[48,82,84],{"class":83},"sMAXC",": ",[48,86,88],{"class":87},"sTRMh","minos\n",[17,90,91,92,95,96,99],{},"minos handles config the same way Hueman does — it ships with ",[45,93,94],{},"_config.yml.example"," but not ",[45,97,98],{},"themes\u002F_config.yml",", so you need to copy it:",[38,101,103],{"className":40,"code":102,"language":42,"meta":43,"style":43},"cp themes\u002Fminos\u002F_config.yml.example themes\u002Fminos\u002F_config.yml\n",[45,104,105],{"__ignoreMap":43},[48,106,107],{"class":50,"line":51},[48,108,102],{},[17,110,111,112,115],{},"Now if you try ",[45,113,114],{},"hexo s",", you'll hit an error:",[17,117,118],{},[30,119],{"alt":120,"src":121},"ERROR Package hexo-renderer-sass is not installed.","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-21%2011.43.11.png",[17,123,124],{},"minos needs a couple of extra packages to run properly. Install them:",[38,126,128],{"className":40,"code":127,"language":42,"meta":43,"style":43},"npm install --save hexo-renderer-sass cheerio\n",[45,129,130],{"__ignoreMap":43},[48,131,132],{"class":50,"line":51},[48,133,127],{},[17,135,136],{},"Now the dev server runs fine.",[17,138,139],{},[30,140],{"alt":67,"src":141},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-21%2012.03.07.png",[12,143,145],{"id":144},"minos-config","minos config",[17,147,148,149,152,153,156],{},"minos's config is on the short side, so I'll skip a full walkthrough. The main bit worth mentioning is language settings. minos switches its language pack based on the filename of ",[45,150,151],{},"theme\u002F_config.yml"," — if you want Traditional Chinese, rename it to ",[45,154,155],{},"theme\u002F_config.zh-tw.yml",".",[17,158,159],{},"minos also supports multiple languages. To set up multi-language config files, run:",[38,161,163],{"className":40,"code":162,"language":42,"meta":43,"style":43},"cp themes\u002Fminos\u002F_config.yml.example themes\u002Fminos\u002F_config.zh-tw.yml\ncp themes\u002Fminos\u002F_config.yml.example themes\u002Fminos\u002F_config.en.yml\n",[45,164,165,170],{"__ignoreMap":43},[48,166,167],{"class":50,"line":51},[48,168,169],{},"cp themes\u002Fminos\u002F_config.yml.example themes\u002Fminos\u002F_config.zh-tw.yml\n",[48,171,173],{"class":50,"line":172},2,[48,174,175],{},"cp themes\u002Fminos\u002F_config.yml.example themes\u002Fminos\u002F_config.en.yml\n",[17,177,178,179,182,183,186,187,190],{},"You can leave ",[45,180,181],{},"themes\u002F_config.en.yml"," alone since the defaults are English. The one you'll edit is ",[45,184,185],{},"themes\u002F_config.zh-tw.yml",". Open it, search for ",[45,188,189],{},"# Navigation bar menu links.",", and update like this:",[38,192,194],{"className":71,"code":193,"language":73,"meta":43,"style":43},"# Navigation bar menu links.\nmenu:\n  歸檔: \u002Fzh-tw\u002Farchives\n  分類: \u002Fzh-tw\u002Fcategories\n  標籤: \u002Fzh-tw\u002Ftags\n  行程: \u002Fzh-tw\u002Fschedule\n  關於: \u002Fzh-tw\u002Fabout\n  好友: \u002Fzh-tw\u002Ffriends\n",[45,195,196,202,210,221,232,243,254,265],{"__ignoreMap":43},[48,197,198],{"class":50,"line":51},[48,199,201],{"class":200},"sQrFR","# Navigation bar menu links.\n",[48,203,204,207],{"class":50,"line":172},[48,205,206],{"class":80},"menu",[48,208,209],{"class":83},":\n",[48,211,213,216,218],{"class":50,"line":212},3,[48,214,215],{"class":80},"  歸檔",[48,217,84],{"class":83},[48,219,220],{"class":87},"\u002Fzh-tw\u002Farchives\n",[48,222,224,227,229],{"class":50,"line":223},4,[48,225,226],{"class":80},"  分類",[48,228,84],{"class":83},[48,230,231],{"class":87},"\u002Fzh-tw\u002Fcategories\n",[48,233,235,238,240],{"class":50,"line":234},5,[48,236,237],{"class":80},"  標籤",[48,239,84],{"class":83},[48,241,242],{"class":87},"\u002Fzh-tw\u002Ftags\n",[48,244,246,249,251],{"class":50,"line":245},6,[48,247,248],{"class":80},"  行程",[48,250,84],{"class":83},[48,252,253],{"class":87},"\u002Fzh-tw\u002Fschedule\n",[48,255,257,260,262],{"class":50,"line":256},7,[48,258,259],{"class":80},"  關於",[48,261,84],{"class":83},[48,263,264],{"class":87},"\u002Fzh-tw\u002Fabout\n",[48,266,268,271,273],{"class":50,"line":267},8,[48,269,270],{"class":80},"  好友",[48,272,84],{"class":83},[48,274,275],{"class":87},"\u002Fzh-tw\u002Ffriends\n",[17,277,278,279,282,283,286,287,290],{},"Since we don't have a ",[45,280,281],{},"\u002Fzh-tw\u002F"," folder or the pages under it yet, remember to create a ",[45,284,285],{},"zh-tw"," folder under ",[45,288,289],{},"_posts"," and add the pages there.",[17,292,293],{},[30,294],{"alt":295,"src":296},"zh-tw pages","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-25%2009.56.56.png",[17,298,299],{},"And that's your basic multi-language blog set up.",[17,301,302,303,310],{},"A well-known minos user is ",[304,305,309],"a",{"href":306,"rel":307},"https:\u002F\u002Fblog.huli.tw\u002F",[308],"nofollow","Huli"," — check out his site before deciding if this theme's for you.",[12,312,314],{"id":313},"a-small-minos-quirk","A small minos quirk",[17,316,317,318,321,322,325,326,64,328,156],{},"You might notice the time under article titles shows up in Simplified Chinese: \"x 个月前 x 分钟 讀完 (約 xxx 字)\". The fix is in ",[45,319,320],{},"minos\u002Fscripts\u002F99_content.js",". Find the variable ",[45,323,324],{},"MOMENTJS_SUPPORTED_LANGUAGES"," and change ",[45,327,285],{},[45,329,330],{},"zh-TW",[17,332,333],{},[30,334],{"alt":335,"src":336},"Traditional Chinese","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-25%2015.19.50.png",[17,338,339,340,343,344,346],{},"Not sure exactly why this happens (didn't dig in), probably a locale-matching issue. minos pulls the ",[45,341,342],{},"language"," field from ",[45,345,63],{}," to figure out which language pack to use. Fix is fix — moving on.",[17,348,349,350],{},"See you in the next one ",[351,352],"d",{},[354,355,356],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html pre.shiki code .sQrFR, html code.shiki .sQrFR{--shiki-default:#BDC4CC}",{"title":43,"searchDepth":172,"depth":172,"links":358},[359,360,361,362],{"id":14,"depth":172,"text":15},{"id":22,"depth":172,"text":23},{"id":144,"depth":172,"text":145},{"id":313,"depth":172,"text":314},"Hexo","2020-09-29 00:00:02","md","en",{},true,"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002Flearn-hexo-16-minos-theme","2",{"title":6,"description":19},false,"en\u002FHexo\u002Flearn-hexo-16-minos-theme",[363,375,376,67],"Learning Hexo from Scratch","iThome Ironman 2020",null